### Running and Testing

**Using Poetry (Mac/Linux):**
```bash
# Run single ticker analysis
poetry run python src/main.py --ticker AAPL

# Test with multiple agents
poetry run python src/main.py --ticker AAPL,MSFT,NVDA

# Backtesting 
poetry run python src/backtester.py --ticker AAPL --start-date 2024-01-01

# Use local models
poetry run python src/main.py --ticker AAPL --ollama
```

**Using pip (Windows recommended):**
```bash
# Run single ticker analysis
.venv/Scripts/python.exe -m src.main --ticker AAPL

# Test with multiple agents  
.venv/Scripts/python.exe -m src.main --ticker AAPL,MSFT,NVDA

# Backtesting with CLI arguments (avoids interactive prompts)
.venv/Scripts/python.exe -m src.backtester --tickers AAPL --start-date 2024-01-01 --end-date 2024-01-15 --analysts-all --model gpt-4o-mini

# Use local models (Ollama detected: qwen3-coder:30b, deepseek-r1:14b, deepseek-r1:latest)
.venv/Scripts/python.exe -m src.main --ticker AAPL --ollama

# With date range
.venv/Scripts/python.exe -m src.main --ticker AAPL --start-date 2024-01-01 --end-date 2024-03-01
```

